      <title>BCI 称私人信贷违约将清除“旅游投资者”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/private-credit-defaults-will-purge-tourist-investors-bci-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不列颠哥伦比亚投资管理公司 (British Columbia Investment Management Corp.) 预计，未来几个月违约率将上升，从而将“旅游投资者”从 1.7 万亿美元的私人信贷市场中赶出去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/private-credit-defaults-will-purge-tourist-investors-bci-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 15:54:03 GMT</pubDate>
