      <title>NextEra 将在美国南部增加 4.5 千兆瓦太阳能和储能设施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/nextera-and-entergy-to-build-4-5-gigawatts-of-solar-batteries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[清洁能源巨头 NextEra Energy Inc. 旗下的一个子公司将与 Entergy Corp. 达成协议，开发多达 4.5 千兆瓦的新太阳能和能源存储项目，押注可再生能源来满足急剧增长的电力需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/nextera-and-entergy-to-build-4-5-gigawatts-of-solar-batteries</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 12:24:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
